# Build artifacts — markdown sources, main.tex, and references.bib are
# the canonical source of truth. The build/ directory is fully derived
# (regenerated on every `make pdf`) and should never be committed.
#
# Note: paper/paper.pdf is intentionally *not* gitignored — it's the
# manually-promoted draft snapshot (via `make snapshot`) that gives
# casual readers a one-click preview without needing a local LaTeX
# install. Update via `make snapshot` at meaningful checkpoints.
build/

# Editor cruft that sometimes appears alongside LaTeX
*.synctex.gz
*.aux
*.log
*.out
*.toc
*.bbl
*.blg
*.fls
*.fdb_latexmk

# biblatex/biber intermediates
*.bcf
*.run.xml
